潛伏力，衹<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">要組織和指揮得當，能使日本軍隊一天忙碌二十四小時，使之疲於奔命</span></span>。 必須記住這個戰爭是在中國打的，這就是說，日軍要完全被敵對的中國人所包圍﹔日軍要被迫運來他們所需的軍用品，而且要自己看守﹔他們要用重兵去保護 交通線，時時謹防襲擊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:36:02.000Z","msg":"完全適用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc6c328fddd75ec975e5bcfe1dfdbeaaabc6b64","tid":1393736,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1678386190a495aefe57c9caeac0ad11bc0103d","tid":1393736,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"有用<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">五大訴求 缺一不可 八月五日 全民三罷</code></pre>"},{"pid":"ab465864dd67ccf3f040213290ba4ea63830f20f","tid":1393736,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:58:54.000Z","msg":"毛魔講抗爭你要聽"},{"pid":"db988ebd602fa258e9d5b761047fdcbcf0bb15f6","tid":1393736,"uid":280555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:03:18.000Z","msg":"推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362a036c7c5c4716ba9032d1699902325e72d16b","tid":1393736,"uid":86270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:03:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bc6766932eca81101d35edc5d8c321efbf76b67f","tid":1393736,"uid":73948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b15cb4217fe73782d47036234dba0cdcb6bcd40","tid":1393736,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:15:36.000Z","msg":"抗日贏係因為日本搞鳩美國，美國不能獨善其身，加上美國有原子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji